HEADWORD: Water rat
<hw>Wa"ter rat`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <sn>1.</sn> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<sd>(a)</sd> <def>The water vole. See under <er>Vole</er>.</def>
<sd>(b)</sd> <def>The muskrat.</def> <sd>(c)</sd> <def>The beaver rat.
See under <er>Beaver</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A thief on the water; a pirate.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Water rate</ent>⟦br⟧
